{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":968,"text":"I visit the future for a living."},{"time":4265,"text":"Not just one future,"},{"time":5915,"text":"but many possible futures,"},{"time":8185,"text":"bringing back evidences from those futures\nfor you to experience today."},{"time":13197,"text":"Like an archaeologist of the future."},{"time":16432,"text":"Over the years, my many journeys\nhave brought back things"},{"time":19188,"text":"like a new species\nof synthetically engineered bees;"},{"time":25052,"text":"a book named, \"Pets as Protein;\""},{"time":28263,"text":"a machine that makes you rich\nby trading your genetic data;"},{"time":31451,"text":"a lamp powered by sugar;"},{"time":34045,"text":"a computer for growing food."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36573,"text":"OK, so I don't actually travel\nto different futures -- yet."},{"time":40988,"text":"But my husband Jon and I spend\na lot of time thinking"},{"time":43951,"text":"and creating visions\nof different futures in our studio."},{"time":48081,"text":"We are constantly looking out\nfor weak signals,"},{"time":50881,"text":"those murmurs of future potential."},{"time":53279,"text":"Then we trace those threads of potential\nout into the future, asking:"},{"time":57963,"text":"What might it feel like\nto live in this future?"},{"time":61068,"text":"What might we see, hear and even breathe?"},{"time":65157,"text":"Then we run experiments,\nbuild prototypes, make objects,"},{"time":69630,"text":"bringing aspects of these futures to life,"},{"time":71684,"text":"making them concrete and tangible"},{"time":74020,"text":"so you can really feel the impact\nof those future possibilities"},{"time":78798,"text":"here and now."},{"time":80936,"text":"But this work is not about predictions."},{"time":83761,"text":"It's about creating tools --"},{"time":85792,"text":"tools that can help connect\nour present and our future selves"},{"time":89280,"text":"so we become active participants\nin creating a future we want --"},{"time":93709,"text":"a future that works for all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96758,"text":"So how do we go about doing this?"},{"time":99143,"text":"For a recent project called Drone Aviary,"},{"time":102511,"text":"we were interested in exploring"},{"time":104073,"text":"what it would mean to live\nwith drones in our cities."},{"time":107064,"text":"Drones that have the power\nto see things we can't,"},{"time":109921,"text":"to go places we can't"},{"time":111697,"text":"and to do so with increasing autonomy."},{"time":114734,"text":"But to understand the technology,"},{"time":116348,"text":"getting our hands dirty was crucial."},{"time":118652,"text":"So we built several different\ndrones in our studio."},{"time":121506,"text":"We gave them names, functions\nand then flew them --"},{"time":125395,"text":"but not without difficulty."},{"time":127413,"text":"Things came loose,"},{"time":128826,"text":"GPS signals glitched"},{"time":130470,"text":"and drones crashed."},{"time":132599,"text":"But it was through such experimentation"},{"time":134765,"text":"that we could construct a very\nconcrete and very experiential slice"},{"time":138964,"text":"of one possible future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141613,"text":"So now, let's go to that future."},{"time":144199,"text":"Let's imagine we are living in a city\nwith drones like this one."},{"time":148196,"text":"We call it The Nightwatchman."},{"time":150756,"text":"It patrols the streets, often spotted\nin the evenings and at night."},{"time":155239,"text":"Initially, many of us were annoyed\nby its low, dull hum."},{"time":159144,"text":"But then, like everything else,\nwe got used to it."},{"time":162423,"text":"Now, what if you could see\nthe world through its eyes?"},{"time":166615,"text":"See how it constantly logs\nevery resident of our neighborhood;"},{"time":170961,"text":"logging the kids who play football\nin the no-ballgame area"},{"time":174305,"text":"and marking them as statutory nuisances."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176776,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178237,"text":"And then see how it disperses\nthis other group, who are teenagers,"},{"time":182231,"text":"with the threat of an autonomously\nissued injunction."},{"time":186387,"text":"And then there's this giant\nfloating disc called Madison."},{"time":190203,"text":"Its glaring presence is so overpowering,"},{"time":192447,"text":"I can't help but stare at it."},{"time":195242,"text":"But if feels like each time I look at it,"},{"time":197267,"text":"it knows a little more about me --"},{"time":199914,"text":"like it keeps flashing all these\nBrianair adverts at me,"},{"time":203103,"text":"as if it knows about\nthe holiday I'm planning."},{"time":206479,"text":"I'm not sure if I find this\nmildly entertaining"},{"time":210230,"text":"or just entirely invasive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213684,"text":"Back to the present."},{"time":215611,"text":"In creating this future, we learned a lot."},{"time":218352,"text":"Not just about how these machines work,"},{"time":220982,"text":"but what it would feel like\nto live alongside them."},{"time":224239,"text":"Whilst drones like Madison\nand Nightwatchman,"},{"time":226517,"text":"in these particular forms,"},{"time":228058,"text":"are not real yet,"},{"time":229623,"text":"most elements of a drone future\nare in fact very real today."},{"time":234264,"text":"For instance,"},{"time":235439,"text":"facial recognition systems\nare everywhere --"},{"time":237777,"text":"in our phones, even in our thermostats"},{"time":240211,"text":"and in cameras around our cities --"},{"time":242714,"text":"keeping a record of everything we do,"},{"time":245484,"text":"whether it's an advertisement\nwe glanced at or a protest we attended."},{"time":249693,"text":"These things are here,"},{"time":251387,"text":"and we often don't understand\nhow they work,"},{"time":254135,"text":"and what their consequences could be."},{"time":257279,"text":"And we see this all around us."},{"time":258883,"text":"This difficulty in even imagining"},{"time":260679,"text":"how the consequences of our actions\ntoday will affect our future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265649,"text":"Last year, where I live, in the UK,\nthere was a referendum"},{"time":268558,"text":"where the people could vote\nfor the UK to leave the EU"},{"time":271107,"text":"or stay in the EU,"},{"time":272289,"text":"popularly known as \"Brexit.\""},{"time":274819,"text":"And soon after the results came out,"},{"time":276645,"text":"a word began to surface\ncalled \"Bregret\" --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":279684,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":280748,"text":"describing people who chose to vote\nfor Brexit as a protest,"},{"time":284207,"text":"but without thinking through\nits potential consequences."},{"time":289127,"text":"And this disconnect is evident\nin some of the simplest things."},{"time":293795,"text":"Say you go out for a quick drink."},{"time":295688,"text":"Then you decide\nyou wouldn't mind a few more."},{"time":298446,"text":"You know you'll wake up\nin the morning feeling awful,"},{"time":301090,"text":"but you justify it by saying,"},{"time":302496,"text":"\"The other me in the future\nwill deal with that.\""},{"time":305607,"text":"But as we find out in the morning,"},{"time":307499,"text":"that future \"you\" is you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310454,"text":"When I was growing up in India\nin the late '70s and early '80s,"},{"time":313675,"text":"there was a feeling"},{"time":314850,"text":"that the future both needed to\nand could actually be planned."},{"time":318343,"text":"I remember my parents had to plan\nfor some of the simplest things."},{"time":321627,"text":"When they wanted a telephone in our house,"},{"time":323680,"text":"they needed to order it and then wait --"},{"time":326014,"text":"wait for nearly five years before\nit got installed in our house."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329285,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":330343,"text":"And then if they wanted to call\nmy grandparents who lived in another city,"},{"time":333865,"text":"they needed to book\nsomething called a \"trunk call,\""},{"time":336417,"text":"and then wait again,\nfor hours or even days."},{"time":339298,"text":"And then abruptly, the phone\nwould ring at two in the morning,"},{"time":342259,"text":"and all of us would jump out of our beds\nand gather round the phone,"},{"time":345533,"text":"shrieking into it,\ndiscussing general well-being"},{"time":347872,"text":"at two in the morning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349229,"text":"Today it can feel like things\nare happening too fast --"},{"time":353033,"text":"so fast, that it can\nbecome really difficult"},{"time":355312,"text":"for us to form an understanding\nof our place in history."},{"time":358293,"text":"It creates an overwhelming sense\nof uncertainty and anxiety,"},{"time":361744,"text":"and so, we let the future\njust happen to us."},{"time":366032,"text":"We don't connect with that future \"us.\""},{"time":368528,"text":"We treat our future selves as a stranger,"},{"time":370864,"text":"and the future as a foreign land."},{"time":373735,"text":"It's not a foreign land;"},{"time":374944,"text":"it's unfolding right in front of us,"},{"time":376716,"text":"continually being shaped\nby our actions today."},{"time":379734,"text":"We are that future,"},{"time":381940,"text":"and so I believe fighting\nfor a future we want"},{"time":384794,"text":"is more urgent and necessary\nthan ever before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388297,"text":"We have learned in our work"},{"time":389786,"text":"that one of the most powerful means\nof effecting change"},{"time":393254,"text":"is when people can directly, tangibly\nand emotionally experience"},{"time":397422,"text":"some of the future consequences\nof their actions today."},{"time":401130,"text":"Earlier this year, the government\nof the United Arab Emirates invited us"},{"time":405128,"text":"to help them shape\ntheir country's energy strategy"},{"time":407598,"text":"all the way up to 2050."},{"time":409558,"text":"Based on the government's econometric\ndata, we created this large city model,"},{"time":413840,"text":"and visualized many\npossible futures on it."},{"time":418387,"text":"As I was excitably taking a group\nof government officials"},{"time":421731,"text":"and members of energy companies"},{"time":423292,"text":"through one sustainable\nfuture on our model,"},{"time":425847,"text":"one of the participants told me,"},{"time":428122,"text":"\"I cannot imagine that in the future\npeople will stop driving cars"},{"time":431253,"text":"and start using public transport.\""},{"time":433916,"text":"And then he said,"},{"time":435100,"text":"\"There's no way I can tell my own son\nto stop driving his car.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":439927,"text":"But we were prepared for this reaction."},{"time":443208,"text":"Working with scientists in a chemistry lab\nin my home city in India,"},{"time":446569,"text":"we had created approximate samples"},{"time":448768,"text":"of what the air would be like in 2030\nif our behavior stays the same."},{"time":454493,"text":"And so, I walked the group\nover to this object"},{"time":457910,"text":"that emits vapor from those air samples."},{"time":461494,"text":"Just one whiff of the noxious\npolluted air from 2030"},{"time":465074,"text":"brought home the point\nthat no amount of data can."},{"time":469069,"text":"This is not the future you would want\nyour children to inherit."},{"time":472620,"text":"The next day, the government\nmade a big announcement."},{"time":475209,"text":"They would be investing billions\nof dollars in renewables."},{"time":478396,"text":"We don't know what part our future\nexperiences played in this decision,"},{"time":482799,"text":"but we know that they've changed\ntheir energy policy"},{"time":485315,"text":"to mitigate such a scenario."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486823,"text":"While something like air from the future\nis very effective and tangible,"},{"time":490352,"text":"the trajectory from our present\nto a future consequence"},{"time":493206,"text":"is not always so linear."},{"time":495347,"text":"Even when a technology\nis developed with utopian ideals,"},{"time":498544,"text":"the moment it leaves the laboratory\nand enters the world,"},{"time":501301,"text":"it is subject to forces outside\nof the creators' control."},{"time":505617,"text":"For one particular project,\nwe investigated medical genomics:"},{"time":509875,"text":"the technology of gathering\nand using people's genetic data"},{"time":512990,"text":"to create personalized medicine."},{"time":515268,"text":"We were asking:"},{"time":516670,"text":"What are some of the unintended\nconsequences of linking our genetics"},{"time":520418,"text":"to health care?"},{"time":523175,"text":"To explore this question further,"},{"time":525465,"text":"we created a fictional lawsuit,"},{"time":527914,"text":"and brought it to life through 31 pieces\nof carefully crafted evidence."},{"time":532783,"text":"So we built an illegal genetic clinic,"},{"time":535895,"text":"a DIY carbon dioxide incubator,"},{"time":539102,"text":"and even bought frozen mice on eBay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":542273,"text":"So now let's go to that future\nwhere this lawsuit is unfolding,"},{"time":545452,"text":"and meet the defendant, Arnold Mann."},{"time":548194,"text":"Arnold is being prosecuted\nby this global giant biotech company"},{"time":551783,"text":"called Dynamic Genetics,"},{"time":553627,"text":"because they have evidence"},{"time":555141,"text":"that Arnold has illegally inserted\nthe company's patented genetic material"},{"time":559755,"text":"into his body."},{"time":561273,"text":"How on earth did Arnold manage to do that?"},{"time":564853,"text":"Well, it all started"},{"time":566051,"text":"when Arnold was asked to submit\na saliva sample in this spit kit"},{"time":570258,"text":"to the NHI --"},{"time":571840,"text":"the UK's National Health\nInsurance service."},{"time":575289,"text":"When Arnold received\nhis health insurance bill,"},{"time":578233,"text":"he was shocked and scared"},{"time":579969,"text":"to see that his premiums\nhad gone through the roof,"},{"time":582375,"text":"beyond anything he or his family\ncould ever afford."}]},{"cues":[{"time":585970,"text":"The state's algorithm had scanned\nhis genetic data"},{"time":588675,"text":"and found the risk of a chronic health\ncondition lurking in his DNA."},{"time":593135,"text":"And so Arnold had to start paying\ntoward the potential costs"},{"time":596523,"text":"of that future disease --"},{"time":598223,"text":"potential future disease from today."},{"time":600430,"text":"In that moment of fear and panic,"},{"time":602066,"text":"Arnold slipped through the city"},{"time":603596,"text":"into the dark shadows\nof this illegal clinic for treatment --"},{"time":607457,"text":"a treatment that would modify his DNA"},{"time":609642,"text":"so that the state's algorithm\nwould no longer see him as a risk,"},{"time":613324,"text":"and his insurance premiums\nwould become affordable again."},{"time":616325,"text":"But Arnold was caught."},{"time":618034,"text":"And the legal proceedings in the case\nDynamic Genetics v. Mann began."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622961,"text":"In bringing such a future to life,"},{"time":624677,"text":"what was important to us\nwas that people could actually touch,"},{"time":627655,"text":"see and feel its potential,"},{"time":629757,"text":"because such an immediate and close\nencounter provokes people"},{"time":632776,"text":"to ask the right questions,"},{"time":634816,"text":"questions like:"},{"time":636111,"text":"What are the implications\nof living in a world"},{"time":638321,"text":"where I'm judged on my genetics?"},{"time":641045,"text":"Or: Who might claim ownership\nto my genetic data,"},{"time":644210,"text":"and what might they do with it?"},{"time":646918,"text":"If this feels even slightly\nout-there or farfetched,"},{"time":650051,"text":"today there's a little-known bill\nbeing passed through the American congress"},{"time":653867,"text":"known as HR 1313, Preserving\nEmployee Wellness Programs Act."},{"time":658455,"text":"This bill proposes to amend the Genetic\nInformation Nondiscrimination Act,"},{"time":662959,"text":"popularly known as GINA,"},{"time":664689,"text":"and would allow employers to ask\nabout family medical history"},{"time":668021,"text":"and genetic data"},{"time":669229,"text":"to all employees for the first time."},{"time":672938,"text":"Those who refuse\nwould face large penalties."}]},{"cues":[{"time":677346,"text":"In the work I've shown so far,"},{"time":679124,"text":"whether it was drones or genetic crimes,"},{"time":681311,"text":"these stories describe troubling futures"},{"time":683693,"text":"with the intention of helping us\navoid those futures."},{"time":687004,"text":"But what about what we can't avoid?"},{"time":689577,"text":"Today, especially with climate change,"},{"time":691693,"text":"it looks like we are heading for trouble."},{"time":694151,"text":"And so what we want to do now\nis to prepare for that future"},{"time":697374,"text":"by developing tools and attitudes\nthat can help us find hope --"},{"time":702322,"text":"hope that can inspire action."}]},{"cues":[{"time":704908,"text":"Currently, we are running\nan experiment in our studio."},{"time":707620,"text":"It's a work in progress."},{"time":709539,"text":"Based on climate data projections,"},{"time":711787,"text":"we are exploring a future"},{"time":713367,"text":"where the Western world has moved\nfrom abundance to scarcity."},{"time":716824,"text":"We imagine living in a future city\nwith repeated flooding,"},{"time":720259,"text":"periods with almost\nno food in supermarkets,"},{"time":723020,"text":"economic instabilities,"},{"time":724780,"text":"broken supply chains."},{"time":727111,"text":"What can we do to not just survive,\nbut prosper in such a world?"},{"time":732015,"text":"What food can we eat?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":734163,"text":"To really step inside these questions,"},{"time":736006,"text":"we are building this room in a flat\nin London from 2050."},{"time":740654,"text":"It's like a little time capsule\nthat we reclaimed from the future."},{"time":743994,"text":"We stripped it down to the bare minimum."},{"time":746164,"text":"Everything we lovingly put in our homes,"},{"time":748094,"text":"like flat-panel TVs,"},{"time":749794,"text":"internet-connected fridges"},{"time":751614,"text":"and artisanal furnishings"},{"time":753067,"text":"all had to go."},{"time":754413,"text":"And in its place,\nwe're building food computers"},{"time":757339,"text":"from abandoned, salvaged\nand repurposed materials,"},{"time":760715,"text":"turning today's waste\ninto tomorrow's dinner."},{"time":764707,"text":"For instance,"},{"time":765882,"text":"we've just finished building our first\nfully automated fogponics machine."},{"time":769894,"text":"It uses the technique of fogponics --\nso just fog as a nutrient,"},{"time":773334,"text":"not even water or soil --"},{"time":774937,"text":"to grow things quickly."},{"time":777324,"text":"At the moment,"},{"time":778567,"text":"we have successfully grown tomatoes."},{"time":781254,"text":"But we'll need more food than what\nwe can grow in this small room."},{"time":784705,"text":"So what else could we forage\nfrom the city?"},{"time":787509,"text":"Insects? Pigeons? Foxes?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":793794,"text":"Earlier, we brought back\nair from the future."},{"time":796387,"text":"This time we are bringing\nan entire room from the future,"},{"time":799134,"text":"a room full of hope, tools and tactics"},{"time":801505,"text":"to create positive action\nin hostile conditions."},{"time":805384,"text":"Spending time in this room,"},{"time":806999,"text":"a room that could be our own future home,"},{"time":809086,"text":"makes the consequences\nof climate change and food insecurity"},{"time":812672,"text":"much more immediate and tangible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":817055,"text":"What we're learning through such\nexperiments and our practice"},{"time":820107,"text":"and the people we engage with"},{"time":821622,"text":"is that creating concrete experiences"},{"time":823897,"text":"can bridge the disconnect\nbetween today and tomorrow."},{"time":827761,"text":"By putting ourselves\ninto different possible futures,"},{"time":830679,"text":"by becoming open and willing"},{"time":832265,"text":"to embrace the uncertainty and discomfort\nthat such an act can bring,"},{"time":836629,"text":"we have the opportunity\nto imagine new possibilities."},{"time":840223,"text":"We can find optimistic futures;"},{"time":842151,"text":"we can find paths forward;"},{"time":844016,"text":"we can move beyond hope into action."},{"time":846781,"text":"It means we have the chance\nto change direction,"},{"time":850966,"text":"a chance to have our voices heard,"},{"time":853832,"text":"a chance to write ourselves\ninto a future we want."},{"time":859548,"text":"Other worlds are possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":862469,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":863660,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}